      <p class="text-white/80 mb-6">A licensed <a href="/mortgage-broker-renewal/" class="text-white underline">mortgage broker</a> can read your charge type, penalty clause, and portability rules — free, no obligation.</p>
      <a href="/book-a-call/">
        <button class="rounded-lg bg-warning-100 hover:bg-warning-50 text-gray-900 font-semibold px-8 py-4 text-lg transition-colors">
